<db:para>To run this example, use the following commands on the prompt:</db:para>
<db:section xml:id="using-cmake">
<db:title>Using CMake</db:title>
<db:programlisting language="cpp" role="bad">cmake -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH=path/to/Qt/6.4.0/your_platform -S &amp;lt;source-dir&amp;gt; -B &amp;lt;build-dir&amp;gt; -G Ninja
cd path/to/build/dir
ninja
qml -I imports plugins.qml
</db:programlisting>
<db:para>For more information about building on the command line using CMake, see <db:link xlink:href="cmake-build-on-cmdline.xml">Building projects on the command line</db:link>.</db:para>
</db:section>
<db:section xml:id="using-qmake">
<db:title>Using qmake</db:title>
<db:programlisting language="cpp" role="bad">qmake
make
qml -I imports plugins.qml
</db:programlisting>
</db:section>
